name: Tomato Soup
instructions: Grate the tomatoes and put them in a pot; Add water and bring to a boil; Add salt and pepper and stir; Serve hot.

name: Menemen
instructions: Chop the onion and sauté in a pan; Add chopped tomatoes and cook; Add eggs and stir while cooking; Season with salt and pepper.

name: Rice
instructions: Wash the rice and put it in a pot; Add water and bring to a boil; Add salt and stir; Cook on low heat.

name: Lentil Soup
instructions: Put green lentils in a pot and add water; Chop the onion and carrot and add them; Add salt and pepper and cook; Blend into a puree.
ingredientsParts: Green lentil; Water; Onion; Carrot; Salt; Pepper

name: Pasta Borek
instructions: Spread the phyllo dough on the counter and put boiled pasta on it; Add cheese and parsley and roll the dough; Brush with egg yolk and bake in the oven.
ingredientsParts: Phyllo dough; Pasta; Cheese; Parsley; Egg

name: Pacanga Borek
instructions: Wrap pastirma and kashar cheese in phyllo dough; Fry in hot oil.

name: Chicken Soup with Vermicelli
instructions: Boil the chicken breast and shred it; Put vermicelli and chicken broth in a pot and bring to a boil; Add salt and pepper.
ingredientsParts: Chicken breast; Vermicelli; Chicken broth; Salt; Pepper

name: Apple Cookie
instructions: Cook grated apple with sugar and cinnamon; Take small pieces of dough and put apple mixture inside; Bake in the oven.
